			<div id="body-content">

			<h1 class="entry-title">Working like a startup at IBM</h1>

					

				

				<h2 class="subhead">How a small and passionate team used modern techniques to shift a business on a short timeline.</h2>

			
			

			<div class="entry-meta">				

				
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> 	

					
						<span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" rel="author" href="http://radar.oreilly.com/bhiggins" title="View all posts by Bill Higgins">

						Bill Higgins</a></span> |								

					
				<!-- RSPEAK_STOP -->

				
					<a href="http://twitter.com/BillHiggins"> @BillHiggins</a> |

				
				
					<a href="https://plus.google.com/102681176353085974948/posts"> +Bill Higgins</a> |

				
				
				
					<span class="comments-link utility-items"><a href="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/09/working-like-a-startup-at-ibm.html#comments" title="Comment on Working like a startup at IBM"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="70594 http://radar.oreilly.com/?p=70594">Comments: 4</span></a></span>

					<span class="meta-sep utility-items"> | </span>

					

				
				<span class="entry-date">September 11, 2014</span> 				

			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

			

